{"tid":1859244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲將由武漢回國公民送到聖誕島隔離","createTime":"2020-02-03T07:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:01:32.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90cd2df75a86b5f52346a7ab7351a97a064570cd","tid":1859244,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"澳洲政府開始將由中國武漢返國的公民及永久居民，送到距離本島2700公里的聖誕島隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n首批243人乘坐包機，抵達西澳州的空軍基地後，轉乘另一班機到聖誕島，他們需要在原本用作拘留移民的中心，隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n不少原本滯留武漢的澳洲人，對拘留中心的醫療設施及環境表示質疑，又批評政府要求他們每人支付1000澳元的撤離費。當局後來改口願意承擔費用，並派出由24名醫護人員組成的專家小組到聖誕島。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲至今確診12宗新型肺炎病例，其中3人已經康復，並已經出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506364-20200203.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506364-20200203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=b9b532e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506364-20200203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=48b88e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506364-20200203.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}